sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant Router
    participant CodeLoader as Code Loader
    participant API
    participant Component

    User->>Browser: Click link or call router.push()
    Browser->>Router: Intercept navigation event
    Router->>Browser: History.pushState(newURL)
    Router->>Router: Match route table
    alt Route chunk not loaded
        Router->>CodeLoader: Dynamic import(chunk)
        CodeLoader-->>Router: JS chunk loaded
    end
    Router->>Component: Instantiate route component
    Component->>API: Fetch required data
    API-->>Component: JSON response
    Component->>Browser: Render new view into DOM
    Browser->>User: Display updated page (no full reload)
    Note over Browser,Router: Back/forward handled via popstate event
